    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the legendary S54 inline-six with its high-pressure VANOS system fully serviced and shimmed. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag six-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains structurally flawless with proactive subframe reinforcement and fresh polyurethane bushings throughout. Finished in pristine original paint with a flawless factory-spec interior, this example offers a linear power band and razor-sharp throttle response via its individual throttle bodies. Zero pixel failure on the instrument cluster, no fluid seepage, and a comprehensive service history make this a true collector-grade driver's machine.",
      "price": 48500.0,
