      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-ready vehicle that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in factory condition; the leather retains its original matte finish with no bolster wear, and the buttons show no signs of use. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, accompanied by a complete binder of service records from day one. Every seal is dry, the undercarriage is spotless, and it drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is an investment-grade example for the discerning collector who demands the absolute best.",
